        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What should be in a musician's press kit?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "One-page press kit with: high-res press photos (band + individual, downloadable), 50-100 word bio (short for media), full bio/press release (longer for features), streaming links (Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube), contact/booking info (email, phone, booking agent), tour highlights (past venues, notable shows), press quotes or reviews (social proof), tech rider (for venues, if relevant). One band added downloadable 'Press Kit ZIP' with all photos and bios: downloaded 47 times first month, landed 6 festival bookings. Make it dead simple for press and venues to say yes."
        }
